  h1 Web Starter Kit
  span 0.9.0 beta
  p.
    Web Starter Kit is an opinionated boilerplate for web development. The builder uses a component approach that will make your project easy to maintain and readable. You do not need to spend much time searching for and linking files. The builder uses <a href="https://meyerweb.com/eric/tools/css/reset/" rel="nofollow">reset.css</a> and <a href="https://necolas.github.io/normalize.css/" rel="nofollow">normalize.css</a></p>
